&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;Applicants must be authorized to work for any employer in the country in which the role is being hired. We are unable to sponsor or take over sponsorship of an employment visa at this time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;288&quot; data-end=&quot;662&quot;&gt;Mark43’s mission is to empower communities and their governments with technology that improves safety and quality of life. We build powerful, scalable, and intuitive software that sets a new standard for the tools first responders rely on every day. Our users are diverse, and we are committed to building a team that reflects a wide range of perspectives and experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;664&quot; data-end=&quot;982&quot;&gt;We are looking for an Account Executive to join our growing UK team. This role sits at the forefront of expanding Mark43’s presence in a new and evolving market. You will help bring modern, cloud-based technology to police forces and public safety organisations, shaping how they operate and serve their communities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;984&quot; data-end=&quot;1160&quot;&gt;This is a unique opportunity to define a market, influence adoption of next-generation policing technology, and drive meaningful impact across the UK public safety landscape.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;xti9y5&quot; data-start=&quot;1167&quot; data-end=&quot;1187&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1189&quot; data-end=&quot;1272&quot;&gt;If you were part of our team, here are some things you would have done last week:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1274&quot; data-end=&quot;2121&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;4u2vj8&quot; data-start=&quot;1274&quot; data-end=&quot;1425&quot;&gt;Led conversations with police forces and public safety organisations to understand operational challenges and identify how Mark43 can deliver value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;16jlwvq&quot; data-start=&quot;1426&quot; data-end=&quot;1526&quot;&gt;Built and progressed pipeline by engaging prospective customers across the UK policing ecosystem&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;4wvu5m&quot; data-start=&quot;1527&quot; data-end=&quot;1641&quot;&gt;Navigated complex public sector procurement processes, maintaining momentum and attention to detail throughout&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1xmvss7&quot; data-start=&quot;1642&quot; data-end=&quot;1752&quot;&gt;Partnered with Marketing, Customer Success, and Delivery teams to develop tailored proposals and solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;hkiy1g&quot; data-start=&quot;1753&quot; data-end=&quot;1871&quot;&gt;Represented Mark43 at industry events, building relationships with key stakeholders across policing and government&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;14qu46p&quot; data-start=&quot;1872&quot; data-end=&quot;2005&quot;&gt;Strengthened your understanding of the UK policing landscape, including funding, procurement frameworks, and competitive dynamics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1lxxk2r&quot; data-start=&quot;2006&quot; data-end=&quot;2121&quot;&gt;Collaborated with internal stakeholders and UK leadership to shape go-to-market strategy in a developing region&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;10vyt30&quot; data-start=&quot;2128&quot; data-end=&quot;2150&quot;&gt;What You’ll Need&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;2152&quot; data-end=&quot;2418&quot;&gt;We’re looking for an experienced enterprise seller who can navigate complex public sector sales and build trusted relationships with senior stakeholders. This role requires ownership, resilience, and the ability to operate effectively in a new and evolving market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;2420&quot; data-end=&qu

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;Applicants must be authorized to work for any employer in the country in which the role is being hired. We are unable to sponsor or take over sponsorship of an employment visa at this time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt;Senior Software Engineer – AI-Enabled Engineering&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134245418&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134245529&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:299,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:299}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Mark43’s mission is to empower communities and their governments with new technologies that improve the safety and quality of life for all. We build powerful, scalable, and elegant software that sets a new standard for the tools upon which our first responders rely. Our users are diverse, and we are therefore committed to embracing diversity of thought and experience within our team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Our platform is already trusted by major public safety agencies across North America—including Boston, D.C., Seattle, and the California Highway Patrol—and we’ve recently expanded into the UK with our first customer overseas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Now, we’re entering an exciting new chapter: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Mark43 is building a next-generation AI-augmented engineering team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;. This is a foundational opportunity to help rethink how software is designed, developed, and delivered using intelligent agentic or related tools.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134245418&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134245529&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:299,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:299}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Senior Software Engineer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; to help lead our AI-enabled engineering initiative. You’ll work at the frontier of AI and software development, experimenting with agentic workflows and shaping how AI tools are integrated into every layer of our engineering stack.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This isn’t just about using AI to autocomplete code—it’s about &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;designing and orchestrating systems of AI agents&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; that can plan, write, review, test, and deploy software collaboratively. In essence,

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;Applicants must be authorized to work for any employer in the country in which the role is being hired. We are unable to sponsor or take over sponsorship of an employment visa at this time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;Mark43&#39;s mission is to empower communities and the governments that serve them with technology that improves safety and quality of life for all. We build powerful, scalable and elegant software that sets a new standard for the tools relied upon by police, emergency services and other public safety organisations. Our users are diverse, and we are committed to welcoming a broad range of perspectives, experiences and ways of thinking within our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;We are seeking a highly skilled and empathetic &lt;strong&gt;Business Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; with a strong background in requirements gathering, process analysis, and stakeholder engagement. This role is well suited to someone who is comfortable working with both technical and non-technical audiences, and who enjoys translating complex operational needs into clear, actionable solutions. Over time, this role will require working from our Manchester office or a customer site at least three days per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;Due to the nature of our work with UK public sector organisations, this role is subject to security vetting. Mark43 will sponsor and manage the vetting process, and employment is contingent on the successful candidate obtaining and maintaining NPPV3 clearance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;[li_&amp;amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Collaborate closely with public safety professionals to elicit, document and validate business and functional requirements, translating operational needs into clear specifications for technical teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Lead discovery and scoping activities, facilitating workshops and interviews with stakeholders to define problems, map current-state processes and identify opportunities for improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Produce high-quality documentation including business requirements documents, process maps, user stories and acceptance criteria.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Serve as a senior liaison between customers and internal product and engineering teams, ensuring requirements are clearly understood and delivered solutions meet stakeholder expectations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Support UAT planning and execution, working with customers to define test scenarios, track defects and confirm that delivered solutions meet agreed requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Build and maintain data analytics dashboards and reports that support public safety operations and decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespac

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;Applicants must be authorized to work for any employer in the country in which the role is being hired. We are unable to sponsor or take over sponsorship of an employment visa at this time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 1&quot;&gt;Compliance and Reporting Analyst&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134245418&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134245529&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:322,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:322}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Mark43’s mission is to empower communities and their governments with technology that improves the safety and quality of life for all. We build powerful, scalable, and intuitive public safety software that sets a new standard for the tools first responders rely on every day. Our customers serve diverse communities, and we believe the best solutions come from teams with diverse perspectives, experiences, and backgrounds.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are looking for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Compliance and Reporting Analyst&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;to join our Technical Services team. In this role, you will help public safety agencies successfully navigate the complexities of NIBRS compliance while ensuring their data is&amp;nbsp;accurate, complete, and actionable. You will partner directly with customers to understand their reporting processes,&amp;nbsp;identify&amp;nbsp;opportunities for improvement, and implement solutions that help agencies meet evolving state and federal reporting requirements. Your&amp;nbsp;expertise&amp;nbsp;will have a direct impact on agencies&#39; ability to&amp;nbsp;maintain&amp;nbsp;compliance and make data-driven decisions that support their communities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134245418&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134245529&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:299,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:299}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;If you were part of our team, here are some things you would have done last week:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;1&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559684&amp;quot;:-2,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;Applicants must be authorized to work for any employer in the country in which the role is being hired. We are unable to sponsor or take over sponsorship of an employment visa at this time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Mark43’s mission is to empower communities and their governments with&amp;nbsp;new technologies&amp;nbsp;that improve the safety and quality of life for all. We build powerful, scalable, and elegant software that&amp;nbsp;sets&amp;nbsp;a new standard for the tools upon which our first responders rely. Our users are diverse, and we are therefore committed to embracing diversity of thought and experience within our team.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:-20,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:-20}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Must reside in Illinois&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Customer Experience Manager to join our growing team. The Mark43 Customer Experience team is passionate about serving as the client’s voice and demonstrating the value of our product offerings. The main goals of the team are to foster product adoption and user satisfaction, assist with change management, capture and contextualize product feedback for our engineering and product teams, track issue resolution, explain new feature enhancements, drive renewals/expansions, and mitigate/prioritize any pain points before they become critical issues.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a client-facing role, and you will be working with your clients regularly both in person and virtually. You will be involved in the full spectrum of post-implementation processes and client care. Much of your day to day will be spent learning about our customers’ unique needs and we expect you to absorb information and eventually demonstrate mastery of a client’s workflows and our product offerings. You will be the trusted advisor for the client and the company will lean on you to advocate for the customer&#39;s needs to ensure they are getting what they need to be successful.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you can expect to work on:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advocate for the client to ensure their needs are being met.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participating in pre-implementation activities to establish relationships and domain expertise early in the deployment process.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performing post-implementation tasks, on-site with our clients, while working on a dynamic Customer Experience team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with the Customer Support, Account Management and Implementation teams to ensure a smooth post-implementation experience for our clients.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working with our clients to learn and understand their current workflows.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep diligent records of all client meetings, tasks, and deliverables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Seeking out and nurturing relationships with power-users and influencers within client sites.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tracking user feedback to help influence the product roadmap and maintain communication with clients to resolve product issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Distributing and ensuring completion of client surveys and ultimately responsible for your clients NPS score.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate internally to solve complex problems and work on a diversity of tasks in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with first&amp;nbsp;responders, which&amp;nbsp;is a uniquely satisfying experience.&

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;Applicants must be authorized to work for any employer in the country in which the role is being hired. We are unable to sponsor or take over sponsorship of an employment visa at this time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Mark43’s mission is to empower communities and their governments with&amp;nbsp;new technologies&amp;nbsp;that improve the safety and quality of life for all. We build powerful, scalable, and elegant software that&amp;nbsp;sets&amp;nbsp;a new standard for the tools upon which our first responders rely. Our users are diverse, and we are therefore committed to embracing diversity of thought and experience within our team.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:-20,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:-20}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Must reside in the Northeast&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are looking for a Customer Experience Manager to join our growing team. The Mark43 Customer&amp;nbsp;Experience&amp;nbsp;team is passionate about serving as the client’s voice and&amp;nbsp;demonstrating&amp;nbsp;the value of our product offerings. The main goals of the team are to foster product adoption and user satisfaction, assist with change management, capture and contextualize product feedback for our engineering and product teams, track issue resolution, explain new feature enhancements, drive renewals/expansions, and mitigate/prioritize any pain points before they become critical issues. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:-20,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:-20}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This is a client-facing role, and you will be working with your clients regularly both in person and virtually. You will be involved in the full spectrum of post-implementation processes and client care. Much of your day to day will be spent learning about our customers’ unique needs and we expect you to absorb information and eventually&amp;nbsp;demonstrate&amp;nbsp;mastery of a client’s workflows and our product offerings. You will be the trusted advisor for the&amp;nbsp;client&amp;nbsp;and the company will lean on you to advocate for the customer&#39;s needs to ensure they are getting what they need to be successful.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:-20,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:-20}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;  &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:-20,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:-20}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;What you can expect to work on:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:-20,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:-20}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;35&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;multilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quo

