&lt;li&gt;Collaborated with our data migration contractors, reviewing technical deliverables and providing guidance to help them succeed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Met with a customer’s records management team to understand their legacy data structure and translate it to the Mark43 schema&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dug into a uniquely formatted source database to uncover edge cases and ensure data fidelity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Worked alongside Mark43 deployment, engineering, and product teams to iterate on and improve our migration tooling and process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balanced project timelines and quality standards while maintaining strong relationships with both internal and external stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
