&lt;p&gt;People who thrive on our team also tend to share the following traits:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Curious and resourceful.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;You enjoy figuring out how systems work and how to make them work better.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clear and collaborative.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;You communicate technical details to non-technical stakeholders and work well across teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Committed to quality.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;You take pride in your work and sweat the details.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
