&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;In this role, you will&amp;nbsp;operate&amp;nbsp;at the intersection of&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;platform engineering and developer experience (DevEx)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;. You will design and evolve internal platforms as&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;products&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;, reducing friction across the software development lifecycle while&amp;nbsp;maintaining&amp;nbsp;strong standards for reliability, security, and compliance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
