&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentored fellow data engineers through code reviews, architectural decisions, and technical planning sessions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Led the design and implementation of scalable, secure data pipelines using dbt, Apache Airflow, and SQL&lt;/li&gt;
