&lt;p&gt;Product Designers at Mark43 lead strategically, integrate various systems, champion design ideation, simplify complex workflows by collaborating with stakeholders, advocate for users, and deliver impactful designs for direct users in law enforcement agencies. You will be focusing on one product area, but have an impact on a breathe of various product areas including Computer Aided Dispatch, Records Management, Advanced Analytics/Insights, and mobile applications. We’re looking to have a designer with 7+ years of professional software product design experience, including deep and demonstrable expertise in managing their work autonomously.&lt;/p&gt;
