&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will collaborate with cross-functional teams&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to facilitate design thinking and innovation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will lead design solutions&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;for law enforcement, EMS, firefighters, other first responders, and 911 dispatchers. The design focus will be on enhancing public safety, improving their focus, and minimizing cognitive load through effective information design, intuitive visual designs, dynamic animations, and responsive feedback mechanisms.&lt;/li&gt;
