&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will present design solutions&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to our customers and leadership teams, actively seeking feedback, and iterating quickly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You care deeply about product craftsmanship&lt;/strong&gt; while efficiently prioritizing and completing design tasks, e.g., in Figma, and contribute to design systems and consistent pattern libraries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will drive AI/ML&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;across the product portfolio, from adoption in design methodologies to advancing adoption in the product.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
